a4789a2c-e60f-418b-8e74-769fb3de3829	2025-02-28 18:14:15.327772+00	2025-02-28 18:14:15.327812+00	5	Victoria@kudusigma.com	Victoria	Connecting Through Love	BBGI organization is a real Game Changer, the team's level of engagement and commitment to this great initiatives is that of a higher value and standard . As a first time visitor, l found it very easy to engage and connect. I am also challenged by the level of authenticity and vulnerability, very encouraging and thoughts provoking.	\N	37eb4c3f-58c3-4845-9d42-8ec91dc7452e
